sponsibility%20for%20my%20actions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20three-page%20letter%20to%20the%20Manhattan%20judge%20who%20presided%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-verdict-frank-startup-guilty-jpmorgan-fraud-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eover%20her%20March%20trial%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20who%20is%20due%20to%20sentence%20her%20on%20September%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20excuses%2C%20only%20regret%20%E2%80%94%20I%20am%20truly%20sorry%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20to%20US%20District%20Judge%20Alvin%20K.%20Hellerstein.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice's%20letter%20touches%20on%20many%20of%20the%20same%20themes%20her%20lawyers%20raised%20earlier%20this%20week%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrank-founder-charlie-javice-fertility-struggles-no-prison-bid-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epre-sentencing%20package%20of%20arguments%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20support%20letters%2C%20some%20300%20pages%20in%20length.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20in%20Friday's%20personal%20letter%20to%20Hellerstein%2C%20Javice%20mentioned%20her%20lifelong%20commitment%20to%20charitable%20works%2C%20her%20yearning%20to%20become%20a%20mother%2C%20and%20her%20Holocaust-surviving%20grandmother.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20expressed%20her%20hope%20that%20a%20mistake%20made%20in%20her%2020s%20would%20not%20ruin%20the%20rest%20of%20her%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20last%20five%20years%20have%20been%20defined%20by%20pain%20and%20loss%20%E2%80%94%20of%20my%20company%2C%20my%20career%2C%20my%20reputation%2C%20and%20many%20friendships%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMost%20painfully%2C%20I%20have%20lost%20time.%20At%2029%2C%20I%20put%20my%20life%20on%20hold%2C%20including%20my%20hopes%20of%20becoming%20a%20young%20mother.%20While%20I%20still%20hope%20motherhood%20is%20in%20the%20cards%20for%20me%2C%20at%20this%20point%20I%20realize%20it%20is%20not%20guaranteed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdjusting%20to%20this%20reality%20as%20I%20approach%20the%20age%20of%2034%20has%20been%20crushingly%20sad%20not%20only%20to%20me%20but%20also%20to%20my%20aging%20parents.%20My%20mom%20is%20now%20approaching%20the%20age%20at%20which%20my%20grandmother%20and%20great-grandmother%20were%20diagnosed%20with%20pancreatic%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thought%20of%20not%20being%20there%20for%20my%20mom%2C%20or%20of%20not%20being%20able%20to%20give%20her%20grandchildren%2C%20is%20unbearable%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice%20was%2029%20years%20old%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202021%20when%20JPMorgan%20acquired%20her%20website%2C%20which%20offered%20students%20financial%20advice%20and%20a%20simplified%20platform%20for%20filling%20out%20their%20FAFSAs%2C%20the%20Free%20Application%20for%20Federal%20Student%20Aid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJavice%2C%20now%2033%2C%20faces%20a%20potential%20maximum%20sentence%20of%2030%20years%20in%20prison%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-frank-fintech-startup-jp-morgan-fraud-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eusing%20fake%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20trick%20the%20largest%20US%20bank%20into%20splurging%20on%20the%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20found%20she%20used%20spreadsheets%20filled%20with%20bogus%20data%20to%20convince%20JPMorgan%20that%20she%20had%20contact%20info%20and%20financial%20data%20for%20over%204%20million%20students%2C%20young%20people%20at%20the%20start%20of%20their%20banking%20journeys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20had%20hoped%20to%20market%20financial%20services%20to%20these%20students%2C%20but%20quickly%20discovered%20it%20had%20overpaid%3A%20Javice's%20website%20only%20had%20data%20for%20300%2C000%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJurors%20needed%20just%20eight%20hours%20of%20deliberation%20over%20two%20days%20to%20convict%20her%20and%20her%20second%20in%20command%20at%20Frank%2C%20Olivier%20Amar%2C%20of%20conspiracy%20to%20commit%20securities%20and%20wire%20fraud%20and%20separate%20charges%20of%20bank%2C%20wire%2C%20and%20securities%20fraud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20ask%20for%20forgiveness%20or%20to%20erase%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Javice%20wrote%20in%20the%20letter%20made%20public%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20ask%20only%20for%20the%20chance%20to%20rebuild%2C%20to%20honor%20the%20support%20I've%20received%2C%20and%20to%20demonstrate%20through%20my%20actions%20that%20grace%20can%20be%20earned%20and%20hope%20%E2%80%94%20however%20fragile%20%E2%80%94%20is%20always%20worth%20embracing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20told%20the%20judge%20that%20whatever%20her%20sentence%20may%20be%2C%20she%20will%20serve%20it%20%26quot%3Bwith%20dignity%20and%20grace.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20learned%20from%20my%20mistakes%20and%20promise%20to%20do%20better%20and%20to%20be%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20width%3D%5C%228.5%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fembed.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F26090941-us-v-javice-defendant-sentencing-letter-20250912%2F%3Fembed%3D1%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%2211%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-takes-full-responsibility-ahead-of-fraud-sentencing-2025-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757718792000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6792ba1b2fcded5e90748a80%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcharlie-javice-takes-full-responsibility-ahead-of-fraud-sentencing-2025-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThere%20are%20no%20excuses%2C%20only%20regret%2C%26quot%3B%20Javice%20wrote%20her%20