20blanket%20rather%20than%20only%20personal-sized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dceb57b2-2160-4d40-9613-abc1ee6f51d0%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20we%20like%5C%22%3EWhat%20we%20like%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223786%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20packaging%20of%20the%20YNM%20weighted%20blanket%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c4340e57d362d375e80d87%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222781%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20YnM%20weightetd%20blanket%20comes%20in%20a%20zippered%20bag%20for%20easy%20storage.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cbc62bdb-aab9-4627-9860-291cda2ec4e5%5C%22%3EThe%20design%20is%20simple%20yet%20effective%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20YnM%20blanket%20is%20thin%20and%20compact%20enough%20to%20be%20unobtrusive%20if%20you%20choose%20to%20keep%20it%20underneath%20a%20larger%20comforter.%20It%20has%20what%20the%20company%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bunique%20seven-layer%20system%26quot%3B%20designed%20to%20comfortably%20surround%20your%20body%20and%20conform%20to%20your%20shape.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cotton%20shell%20is%20filled%20with%20glass%20beads%20for%20even%20pressure.%20The%20beads%20are%20inside%20a%20baffle-box-constructed%20blanket%2C%20so%20the%20weight%20is%20evenly%20distributed%20and%20doesn't%20require%20frequent%20rearrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bc14bf9d-c822-4dc4-ac95-c4ab2ca3c144%5C%22%3EIt%20helped%20us%20sleep%20better%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20didn't%20know%20how%20much%20of%20an%20improvement%20there%20was%20to%20make%20in%20my%20sleep%20until%20I%20started%20using%20weighted%20blankets.%20I%20admittedly%20love%20comfort%20more%20than%20the%20average%20person%2C%20but%20I'd%20call%20them%20one%20of%20the%20few%20products%20that%20bring%20me%20closest%20to%20the%20high%20bar%20of%20genuine%20%26quot%3Bjoy%26quot%3B%20Marie%20Kondo%20famously%20uses%20as%20a%20selective%20litmus%20test%20for%20possessions%20you%20should%20keep%20or%20throw%20out.%20When%20used%20for%20relaxation%2C%20I%20feel%20cozy.%20At%20night%2C%20I%20fall%20asleep%20faster%2C%20sleep%20deeper%2C%20and%20feel%20more%20refreshed%20the%20next%20day.%20When%20I'm%20traveling%2C%20I%20miss%20it.%20I've%20recommended%20it%20to%20friends%20who%20suffer%20from%20insomnia%20and%20heard%20similarly%20enthusiastic%20feedback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2C%20a%20home%20and%20sleep%20reviews%20fellow%2C%20also%20tested%20the%20YnM%20weighted%20blanket%20and%20reported%20that%20it%20soothed%20her%20to%20sleep%20every%20night.%20She%20said%20that%20the%20pressure%20was%20noticeable%20but%20not%20uncomfortable%2C%20instead%20resulting%20in%20a%20swaddled%20feeling%20that%20she%20enjoyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2235ec6225-0f46-4868-9469-7674ea3cca3d%5C%22%3EThere's%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20sizes%2C%20colors%2C%20and%20weights%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20YnM%20blanket%20is%20notable%20for%20coming%20in%20sizes%20big%20enough%20to%20cover%20your%20entire%20bed%20or%20be%20shared%20as%20a%20couple.%20It's%20sold%20in%20a%20traditional%20throw%20size%2C%20but%20you'll%20also%20find%20larger%20blankets%20that%20can%20cover%20an%20entire%20king-size%20bed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20plus-size%20person%2C%20Searles%20finds%20it%20difficult%20to%20find%20a%20weighted%20blanket%20at%20the%20recommended%2010%25%20of%20her%20body%20weight%2C%20but%20YnM%20sells%20blankets%20as%20heavy%20as%2050%20pounds.%20There%20are%20also%20small%20versions%20as%20light%20as%20five%20pounds%20%E2%80%94%20a%20perfect%20size%20for%20kids.%20She%20appreciates%20the%20wide%20range%20of%20weights%2C%20so%20everyone%20is%20comfortable%20using%20this%20blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20whopping%2034%20options%2C%20there's%20a%20huge%20color%20range%2C%20too.%20If%20none%20of%20the%20colors%20strike%20your%20fancy%2C%20we%20recommend%20inserting%20the%20blanket%20into%20a%20duvet%20cover.%20Conveniently%2C%20the%20king-size%20blanket%20comes%20with%20a%20matching%20duvet%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226c85f0ac-5c4e-42a9-a614-69756f54433a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20we%20don't%20like%5C%22%3EWhat%20we%20don't%20like%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20only%20complaint%20with%20weighted%20blankets%20is%20that%20they%20can%20work%20too%20well.%20My%20sleep%20is%20deeper%20and%20more%20satisfying%2C%20but%20that%20can%20be%20accompanied%20by%20a%20groggier%20morning.%20Instead%20of%20feeling%20fully%20awake%20when%20my%20alarm%20goes%20off%2C%20getting%20adjusted%20to%20the%20day%20can%20be%20more%20difficult.%20Having%20said%20that%2C%20this%20is%20a%20con%20I'm%20fine%20living%20with%20for%20better%20sleep%20and%20more%20stable%20energy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESearles%20found%20that%20the%20blanket%20slept%20hot%2C%20leading%20to%20overheating%20at%20night%2C%20so%20we%20wouldn't%20recommend%20it%20for%20hot%20sleepers.%20Also%2C%20while%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20sizes%2C%20weights%2C%20and%20colors%20available%2C%20the%20stock%20of%20each%20fluctuates%20wildly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b42a7a5-6585-484d-b3e8-f5672a9eb189%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blue%20weighted%20blanket%20sits%20on%20a%20bed%20with%20pink%20throw%20pillows.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680bec2ec6ad288d147f391e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20hide%20the%20baffle-box%20construction%2C%20the%20YnM%20blanket%20fits%20snugly%20in%20a%20duvet%20cover.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20in%20all%2C%20YnM's%20weighted%20blanket%20is%20a%20great%20option%3B%20it's%20breathable%2C%20versatile%2C%20uniformly%20weighted%2C%20and%20comes%20on%20the%20less%20expensive%20end%20of%20the%20weight