Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leash%20is%20machine-washable%2C%20but%20I%20found%20stains%20were%20easier%20to%20remove%20by%20hand.%20While%20it%20stands%20up%20well%20to%20dirt%20and%20grime%2C%20it's%20not%20the%20best%20option%20for%20heavy%20leash%20chewers.%20When%20I%20simulated%20chewing%2C%20it%20showed%20damage%20quickly%2C%20but%20this%20was%20the%20case%20with%20most%20nylon%20leashes%20I%20tested.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22501707bf-26db-436a-ad0d-f083f1883794%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20rope%5C%22%3EBest%20rope%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%20and%20foremost%2C%20I%20like%20the%20SassyWoof%20Rope%20Leash%20because%20of%20its%20comfort.%20Made%20entirely%20from%20cotton%2C%20it%20feels%20soft%20on%20my%20hand.%20It's%20also%20substantially%20lighter%20than%20the%20other%20rope%20leashes%20I%20tested%2C%20including%20my%20top%20pick%20for%20the%20best%20multi-function%20leash%2C%20which%20is%20also%20a%20rope%20design.%20Its%20light%20weight%20and%20slim%20profile%20are%20especially%20well-suited%20for%20small%20and%20medium-sized%20dogs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20highlight%20is%20the%20variety%20of%20colors%20available.%20SassyWoof%20offers%20dozens%20of%20options%2C%20including%20bright%20multi-colored%20designs%20and%20softer%20pastels.%20The%20handle%20also%20includes%20a%20convenient%20ring%20for%20attaching%20accessories%20like%20a%20poop%20bag%20holder%20or%20collapsible%20water%20bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20holds%20a%20light%20pink%20SassyWoof%20rope%20leash%20while%20walking%20a%20black%20dog%20with%20a%20white%20patch%20on%20its%20neck%2C%20wearing%20a%20purple%20harness%2C%20along%20a%20paved%20path%20next%20to%20grass.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6511bdcb59fd710019f00220%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20SassyWoof%20leash%20was%20a%20comfortable%20weight%20for%20our%20test%20dog%2C%20who%20wasn't%20bothered%20by%20it%20during%20walks.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20leash%20performed%20reliably%20on%20city%20sidewalk%20strolls%2Cbut%20it's%20less%20ideal%20for%20parks%20or%20open%20areas%20where%20you%20may%20want%20to%20give%20your%20dog%20more%20room%20to%20roam.%20At%205%20feet%2C%20it's%20a%20good%20length%20for%20small%20pups%20but%20a%20bit%20short%20for%20larger%20dogs.%20It%20also%20lacks%20extra%20features%20found%20on%20some%20of%20my%20other%20picks%20for%20the%20best%20dog%20leashes%2C%20like%20multiple%20D-rings%20and%20reflective%20detailing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dc8f4e3b-6a24-48b4-bde1-d34d58629dac%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20hands-free%5C%22%3EBest%20hands-free%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20sought%20a%20waist-worn%20leash%20with%20a%20comfortable%20waistband%2C%20strong%20lead%2C%20and%20easy-to-maneuver%20hardware%20designed%20specifically%20for%20hands-free%20walking.%20The%20Ruffwear%20Crag%20Reflective%20Leash%20delivered%20on%20all%20three.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20section%20that%20wraps%20around%20the%20waist%20is%20padded%20and%20adjustable%2C%20and%20it's%20easy%20to%20convert%20into%20a%20handheld%20leash%20by%20shortening%20the%20straps.%20While%20some%20other%20leashes%20I%20tested%20had%20this%20feature%2C%20the%20transition%20between%20waist-worn%20and%20handheld%20wasn't%20nearly%20as%20seamless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20aspect%20I%20appreciate%20was%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20bungee.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vet.cornell.edu%2Fabout-us%2Fpeople%2Fkatherine-anderson-dvm-acvb%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Katherine%20Anderson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20and%20assistant%20clinical%20professor%20at%20the%20Duffield%20Institute%20for%20Animal%20Behavior%20at%20Cornell%20University%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%2C%20advises%20against%20bungee%20leashes.%20Like%20a%20retractable%20leash%2C%20a%20bungee%20creates%20constant%20tension%20on%20the%20lead%2C%20making%20loose-leash%20walking%20difficult.%20It%20can%20also%20be%20dangerous%2C%20as%20I%20found%20while%20testing%20the%20EzyDog%20Leash.%20The%20bungee%20often%20threw%20me%20off%20balance%2C%20and%20if%20I%20wasn't%20watching%20my%20dog%20closely%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20notice%20she%20was%20pulling%20until%20the%20bungee%20snapped%2C%20which%20would%20drag%20me%20in%20whatever%20direction%20she%20was%20pulling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20holds%20a%20colorful%20Ruffwear%20Crag%20Leash%20with%20a%20blue%20and%20orange%20wave%20pattern%20while%20walking%20a%20black%20dog%20with%20a%20white%20patch%20on%20its%20neck%2C%20wearing%20a%20purple%20harness%2C%20on%20a%20sidewalk%20beside%20grass.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6511bef159fd710019f00283%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWaist-worn%20leashes%20can%20be%20uncomfortable%2C%20but%20the%20Ruffwear%20Crag%20Reflective%20Leash%20was%20great%20to%20wear%20around%20the%20waist%20and%20as%20a%20regular%20handheld%20leash.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20even%20the%20best%20dog%20leashes%20aren't%20perfect%2C%20and%20the%20Crag%20has%20some%20flaws.%20While%20it's%20durable%2C%20it's%20not%20resistant%20to%20staining.%20The%20clip%20attachment%20is%20also%20an%20unusual%20U-shape%2C%20which%20is%20less%20intuitive%20than%20a%20traditional%20C-clip.%20The%20attachment%20was%20also%20quite%20heavy%2C%20enough%20that%20my%20dog%20was%20slightly%20bothered%20by%20it%20at%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b4cfde6b-de9a-456b-907c-58bcdc6a9c75%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20padded%20handle%5C%22%3EBest%20padded%20handle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20walkers%20who%20want%20extra%20hand%20support%2C%20the%20Frisco%20Rope%20Dog%20Leash%20is%20a%20standout%20choice.%20Its%20generously%20padded%20handle%20prevented%20rope%20burn%20and%20discomfort%20in%20all%20of%20my%20pull%20tests%2C%20and%20unlike%20some%20other%20heavily%20padded%20leashes%2C%20the%20handle's%20width%20makes%20it%20comfortable%20for%20most%20hand%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDurability%20was%20another%20strong%20point.%20The%20rope-style%20design%2C%20inspired%20by%20mountain%20climbing%20gear%2C%20made%20the%20leash%20difficult%20to%20puncture%20or%20cut.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20the%20most%20durable%20padded-handle%20leash%20I%20tested%2C%20outperforming%20the%20popular%20Baapet%20Dog%20Leash%20with%20Padded%20Handle%2C%20which%20broke%20during%20my%20very%20first%20pull%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20holds%20a%20black%20Frisco%20rope%20leash%20with%20a%20padded%20handle%20while%20walking%20a%20black%20dog%20with%20a%20white%20patch%20on%20its%20neck%2C%20wearing%20a%20purple%20harness%2C%20on%20a%20cracked%20sidewalk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6511c48d59fd710019f003a2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20padded%20handle%20like%20the%20one%20found%20on%20Frisco's%20Rope%20Dog%20Leash%20can%20make%20walks%20more%20comfortable.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20trade-offs%20are%20similar%20to%20those%20of%20other%20thickly%20padded%20handle%20leashes.%20The%20bulkier%20handle%20isn't%20easy%20to%20tuck%20into%20a%20small%20purse%20or%20pocket%2C%20and%20the%20leash%20lacks%20extra%20attachment%20points%20for%20carrying%20walking%20essentials%20like%20a%20poop%20bag%20holder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22954190f8-f61b-4998-9612-9d4a57719ede%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20long-line%5C%22%3EBest%20long-line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20a%20long-line%20leash%20is%20a%20great%20way%20to%20work%20on%20recall%20or%20give%20your%20dog%20more%20freedom%20to%20roam.%20The%20Mendota%20Long%20Snap%20Leash%20with%20its%2015-foot%20lead%20is%20well-suited%20for%20the%20job.%20It's%20lightweight%2C%20easy%20to%20roll%20and%20extend%20for%20quick%20control%2C%20stain-resistant%2C%20and%20equipped%20with%20straightforward%20hardware.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20rated%20the%20Mendota%20highly%20for%20its%20simplicity.%20Many%20other%20long-line%20leashes%20attempt%20to%20do%20too%20much%2C%20with%20multiple%20adjustment%20points%20or%20extra%20hardware%20that%20makes%20them%20less%20portable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20favorite%20feature%20is%20the%20stain-resistant%20polypropylene%20rope.%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20while%20the%20brand%20says%20it's%20machine%20washable%2C%20it%20tangled%20around%20the%20agitator%20in%20my%20top-load%20washer%20because%20of%20its%20length.%20Rinsing%20it%20under%20the%20faucet%20is%20a%20much%20easier%20cleaning%20method.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20holds%20a%20dark%20green%20rope%20leash%20while%20walking%20a%20black%20dog%20with%20a%20white%20patch%20on%20its%20neck%2C%20wearing%20a%20purple%20harness%2C%20along%20a%20shaded%20sidewalk%20beside%20greenery.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6511c0b559fd710019f002c9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELong%20line%20leashes%20like%20this%20one%20by%20MendotaPet%20can%20be%20a%20good%20option%20to%20let%20your%20dog%20wander%20while%20still%20being%20safe.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20the%20material%20does%20have%20drawbacks.%20It%20frayed%20quickly%20after%20a%20single%20puncture%2C%20making%20it%20a%20poor%20choice%20for%20heavy%20chewers.%20It%20also%20lacks%20extra%20D-rings%20for%20attaching%20accessories.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227bc3efb1-f2ee-43bf-ac68-73bf5ec27672%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20multi-function%5C%22%3EBest%20multi-function%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20multi-function%20leashes%20are%20designed%20for%20versatility%2C%20the%20best%20ones%20need%20to%20adjust%20easily%20to%20different%20situations%2C%20whether%20worn%20around%20the%20waist%2C%20carried%20by%20hand%2C%20used%20as%20a%20double%20clip%2C%20or%20slung%20over%20the%20shoulder.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20liked%20the%20Found%20My%20Animal%20Adjustable%20Leash%20because%20it%20performed%20well%20in%20every%20setup.%20Its%20rope%20material%20was%20strong%20and%20held%20up%20against%20my%20dog's%20pulling%2C%20while%20the%20carabiner%20attachment%20points%20added%20both%20durability%20and%20security.%20Each%20carabiner%20features%20a%20roller%20screw%20covering%20the%20clasp%20for%20extra%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20holds%20a%20tan%20rope%20leash%20with%20brass%20hardware%20while%20walking%20a%20black%20dog%20with%20a%20white%20patch%20on%20its%20neck%2C%20wearing%20a%20purple%20harness%2C%20along%20a%20sidewalk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6511c3e959fd710019f00375%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Found%20My%20Animal%20Leash%20was%20the%20most%20versatile%20leash%20we%20tested%20for%20this%20guide.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20downside%20of%20these%20sturdy%20attachments%20is%20that%20they%20add%20bulk%2C%20making%20the%20leash%20difficult%20to%20tuck%20into%20a%20purse%20or%20pocket.%20It's%20better%20suited%20to%20a%20larger%20bag%20for%20transport.%20The%20leash%20is%20also%20on%20the%20heavier%20side.%20My%2050-pound%20dog%20managed%20fine%2C%20but%20I%20noticed%20the%20weight%20more%20when%20wearing%20it%20over%20my%20shoulder%20or%20around%20my%20waist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ee8415b-ad17-4c58-a742-af8953275e7a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20reflective%5C%22%3EBest%20reflective%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EReflective%20leashes%20increase%20your%20and%20your%20dog's%20visibility%20during%20nighttime%20walks%2C%20which%20is%20especially%20helpful%20when%20crossing%20streets%20or%20walking%20near%20traffic.%20My%20top%20pick%2C%20the%20Chai's%20Choice%20Padded%203M%20Reflective%20Outdoor%20Adventure%20Dog%20Leash%2C%20has%20two%20reflective%20stripes%20woven%20along%20its%20edges%2C%20making%20it%20easy%20to%20see%20in%20low%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20performed%20well%20during%20the%20day%2C%20too.%20It's%20bright%20enough%20to%20stand%20out%20without%20being%20blinding%20in%20direct%20sunlight.%20By%20comparison%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15110410445qjk-20%26h%3D83e725f2ebdb44dd269829a2ddf44f8f2f7867bbf5046508e3f0f6e82881b7eb%26postID%3D68c44c7d60e6df0ae376da94%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fpets%252Fbest-dog-leashes%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.orvis.com%252Fproduct%252Forvis-reflective-dog-leash%252F3JCE.html%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOrvis%20Reflective%20Leash%3C%2Fa%3E%20didn't%20make%20the%20cut%20because%20its%20reflective%20strip%20was%20too%20bright%20during%20daytime%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20person%20holds%20a%20purple%20nylon%20leash%20while%20walking%20a%20black%20dog%20with%20a%20white%20patch%20on%20its%20neck%2C%20wearing%20a%20matching%20purple%20harness%2C%20on%20a%20sidewalk.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6511bce0e2c0220019ef4ff3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222442%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20leash%20was%20reflective%20but%20not%20blinding%20like%20some%20of%20the%20other%20leashes%20we%20tested.%3Cp%3ESophia%20Carlisle%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELightweight%20materials%20also%20make%20the%20Chai's%20Choice%20leash%20one%20of%20the%20most%20comfortable%20I%20tested.%20It%20was%20easy%20to%20hold%20and%20didn't%20bother%20my%20dog%20when%20it%20was%20clipped%20to%20her%20harness.%20The%20handle%20also%20has%20a%20bit%20of%20extra%20padding%20to%20prevent%20rope%20burn.%20I%20noticed%20a%20clear%20difference%20in%20comfort%20between%20the%20padded%20handle%20and%20the%20regular%20mesh%20portion%20of%20the%20leash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20I%20didn't%20like%20about%20this%20leash%20was%20cleaning%20it.%20The%20nylon%20mesh%20material%20was%20difficult%20to%20wash%2C%20and%20stains%20remained%20visible%20even%20after%20both%20machine%20washing%20and%20hand%20scrubbing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228086810a-5b72-4b3d-8483-5efb253f4b7c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20in%20a%20dog%20leash%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20look%20for%5C%22%3ELike%20any%20purchase%20you%20make%20for%20your%20pet%2C%20there%20are%20several%20factors%20to%20consider%20when%20choosing%20a%20leash.%20The%20points%20below%20can%20help%20you%20narrow%20your%20search.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterials%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Dog%20trainers%20recommend%20sturdy%2C%20flexible%20materials%20for%20durability%20and%20comfort.%20Nylon%2C%20leather%2C%20and%20biothane%20are%20classic%20choices%2C%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpupniron.com%2Fabout-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELaurie%20Williams%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20professional%20dog%20trainer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ELength%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20A%20leash%20between%204%20and%206%20feet%20long%20allows%20for%20comfortable%20walking%20with%20a%20loose%20lead%20while%20still%20keeping%20your%20dog%20close%20to%20you.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvetmed.illinois.edu%2F2025%2F01%2F30%2Ffaculty-spotlight-gene-pavlovsky-dvm-dabvp%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Gene%20Pavlovsky%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20veterinarian%20and%20chief%20of%20staff%20for%20the%20Dr.%20John%20A.%20Coyne%20South%20Clinic%20at%20the%20Illinois%20Urbana-Champaign%20College%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%2C%20recommends%20using%20a%20long-line%20leash%20with%20dogs%20that%20are%20reliably%20trained%20and%20will%20come%20when%20called.%20He%20adds%20that%20long%20lines%20are%20best%20used%20in%20quiet%20areas%20with%20few%20people%20or%20animals.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20use%20a%20long-line%20leash%20in%20areas%20where%20there%20are%20few%20other%20people%20or%20other%20animals%20so%20that%20there%20are%20no%20surprises%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20best%20dog%20leashes%20feel%20comfortable%20to%20hold%20and%20do%20not%20cause%20rope%20burn%20or%20skin%20irritation%20if%20your%20dog%20pulls.%20Just%20as%20important%2C%20it%20should%20support%20loose-leash%20walking.%20Williams%20says%20that%20if%20a%20leash%20is%20always%20tight%2C%20it%20can%20build%20anxiety%20and%20frustration%2C%20leading%20to%20negative%20associations%20with%20walks.%20She%20emphasizes%20using%20positive%20reinforcement%20training%20techniques%20as%20one%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20teach%20dogs%20to%20walk%20calmly%20on%20a%20loose%20lead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAttachment%20point%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vet.upenn.edu%2Fpeople%2Ffaculty-clinician-search%2FCARLOSIRACUSA%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Carlo%20Siracusa%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20board-certified%20veterinary%20behaviorist%20and%20professor%20of%20clinical%20small%20animal%20behavior%20and%20welfare%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Pennsylvania%20School%20of%20Veterinary%20Medicine%2C%20says%20that%20the%20leash's%20attachment%20point%20%E2%80%94%20where%20one%20would%20connect%20the%20leash%20to%20the%20harness%20%E2%80%94%20should%20be%20strong%20enough%20to%20withstand%20pulling%20and%20easy%20to%20unclip.%20In%20my%20testing%2C%20C-clips%20and%20carabiners%20proved%20both%20sturdy%20and%20quick%20to%20remove%2C%20while%20other%20types%20scored%20lower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdditional%20safety%20features%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Reflective%20material%20and%20traffic%20handles%20aren't%20essential%20but%20can%20be%20useful%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20dog's%20needs%20and%20where%20you%20walk.%20These%20features%20make%20it%20easier%20to%20keep%20your%20dog%20visible%20and%20under%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221bc7f6ff-df38-4a11-9162-aa244e4433fe%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20avoid%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20avoid%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it's%20important%20to%20know%20what%20makes%20a%20great%20leash%2C%20there%20are%20also%20features%20best%20avoided.%20%26quot%3BGenerally%20speaking%2C%20the%20leash%20should%20be%20durable%2C%20comfortable%2C%20secure%2C%20and%20easy%20to%20attach%2C%26quot%3B%20Pavlovsky%20says.%20If%20a%20leash%20lacks%20these%20qualities%2C%20it%20might%20not%20be%20a%20good%20choice.%20Here%20are%20a%20few%20more%20points%20to%20consider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20leash%20that's%20too%20heavy%20can%20be%20uncomfortable%20for%20your%20dog%2C%20especially%20when%20used%20with%20a%20back-clip%20harness.%20A%20lightweight%20option%20is%20often%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERetractable%20or%20bungee%20leashes%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Though%20popular%2C%20these%20leashes%20create%20constant%20tension%2C%20which%20Anderson%20says%20isn't%20good%20for%20dogs.%20Retractable%20leashes%20also%20pose%20risks%20for%20handlers%2C%20with%20users%20reporting%20rope%20burns%2C%20cuts%2C%20and%20other%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWaist-worn%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20These%20can%20be%20convenient%20for%20walkers%20confident%20in%20their%20balance%2C%20but%20Williams%20says%20they%20aren't%20ideal%20for%20everyone.%20Large%2C%20strong%20dogs%20may%20pull%20hard%20enough%20to%20drag%20their%20owners%2C%20making%20this%20style%20risky%20in%20those%20situations.%20The%20physical%20mobility%20of%20the%20owner%20is%20very%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Williams.%20%26quot%3BSome%20people%20might%20not%20be%20in%20the%20physical%20condition%20to%20use%20those%2C%20so%20everybody%20has%20to%20be%20smart%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221776d321-1bc0-4077-8491-e5bed34e78b7%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20dog%20leashes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EI%20consulted%20four%20experts%20to%20learn%20what%20matters%20most%20in%20a%20leash.%20including%20qualities%20like%20durable%20materials%20and%20the%20ideal%20length.%20Guided%20by%20their%20advice%2C%20I%20tested%2020%20leashes%20in%20real-world%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20two%20weeks%2C%20I%20tested%20the%20leashes%20with%20Lyla%2C%20my%2050-pound%20pit%20mix.%20Each%20leash%20was%20used%20for%20at%20least%2015%20minutes%20and%20up%20to%20an%20hour%20in%20different%20situations%3A%20daytime%20street%20walks%2C%20nighttime%20park%20strolls%2C%20and%20evening%20walks%20in%20high-traffic%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20I%20also%20evaluated%20each%20leash%20on%20the%20following%20criteria%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterials%20and%20durability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20recorded%20the%20materials%20used%20and%20how%20they%20performed%20in%20pull%20and%20chewing%20tests.%20To%20evaluate%20the%20material's%20strength%2C%20another%20person%20yanked%20the%20leash%20multiple%20times%20while%20it%20was%20attached%20to%20my%20waist%20or%20held%20in%20my%20hand.%20I%20also%20performed%20a%20mallet%20test%20on%20the%20attachment%20point%20and%20fabric.%20Finally%2C%20I%20tried%20to%20puncture%20and%20cut%20the%20leashes%20with%20dull%20scissors%20to%20simulate%20chewing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESafety%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Durability%20is%20an%20important%20factor%20in%20evaluating%20safety.%20After%20cutting%20and%20puncturing%20the%20leashes%2C%20I%20repeated%20the%20pull%20test%20to%20see%20if%20they%20still%20held%20up.%20I%20also%20checked%20for%20problems%20attaching%20and%20detaching%20the%20leash%20from%20a%20harness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EComfort%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20During%20the%20pull%20test%2C%20I%20looked%20for%20rope%20burn%20or%20skin%20irritation%20and%20noted%20how%20comfortable%20each%20leash%20felt%20in%20my%20hand.%20I%20also%20observed%20whether%20Lyla%20appeared%20bothered%20by%20heavy%20hardware%20or%20other%20design%20features%20during%20walks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeight%20and%20width%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20measured%20the%20width%20of%20each%20leash%20to%20further%20identify%20those%20that%20felt%20too%20narrow%20or%20too%20wide%2C%20and%20weighed%20them%20to%20assess%20how%20they%20may%20feel%20to%20hold%20during%20walks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECare%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20smeared%20a%202-inch%20section%20of%20each%20leash%20with%20dirt%20and%20mud%2C%20allowed%20them%20to%20dry%2C%20and%20then%20washed%20them%20by%20hand%20with%20soap%20and%20water.%20I%20noted%20which%20leashes%20retained%20stains%20and%20which%20ones%20cleaned%20up%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVersatility%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20assessed%20how%20many%20ways%20each%20leash%20could%20be%20used%20and%20which%20environments%20it%20was%20best%20suited%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20secondary%20factors%2C%20I%20also%20considered%20each%20leash's%20color%20options%2C%20length%2C%20portability%2C%20and%20any%20additional%20attachments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226e8ac506-4b93-417a-a18a-5dfcdf480e5b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EDog%20leash%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20best%20dog%20leash%20to%20use%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20leash%20depends%20on%20the%20needs%20of%20both%20the%20dog%20and%20the%20owner.%20In%20general%2C%20look%20for%20a%20strong%20clip%2C%20a%20comfortable%20handle%2C%20and%20durable%20materials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20leash%20is%20safest%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20dog%20trainer%20Williams%2C%20the%20safest%20leash%20is%20one%20that's%20comfortable%20for%20both%20you%20and%20your%20dog.%20While%20length%20and%20functionality%20matter%2C%20comfort%20helps%20prevent%20negative%20experiences%20for%20both%20you%20and%20your%20dog.%20Avoid%20leashes%20that%20can%20cause%20abrasions%20on%20your%20hands%2C%20and%20look%20for%20secure%2C%20sturdy%20attachment%20points.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20leash%20should%20I%20use%20for%20training%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWilliams%20recommends%20a%20standard%204-%20to%206-foot%20leash%20for%20leash%20training.%20A%20long-line%20leash%20works%20well%20for%20recall%20practice%2C%20but%20it%20should%20only%20be%20used%20in%20uncrowded%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20I%20leash%20train%20a%20dog%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20leash%20is%20an%20essential%20safety%20tool%2C%20but%20not%20all%20dogs%20instinctively%20know%20how%20to%20walk%20with%20one.%20Williams%20says%20training%20should%20always%20be%20positive.%20%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20want%20your%20puppy%20to%20right%20away%20form%20a%20negative%20association%20with%20the%20leash%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20A%20good%20starting%20point%20is%20to%20practice%20indoors.%20Before%20attaching%20a%20leash%20to%20your%20dog%2C%20feed%20your%20dog%20their%20breakfast%20as%20they%20walk%20through%20the%20house.%20This%20allows%20a%20dog%20to%20associate%20walking%20with%20you%20as%20something%20positive%20and%20enjoyable.%20Williams%20says%20to%20add%20the%20leash%20only%20later%20when%20your%20dog%20is%20comfortable%20walking%20along%20with%20you.%20This%20gradual%20approach%20reduces%20the%20risk%20of%20your%20dog%20forming%20negative%20associations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20are%20retractable%20leashes%20bad%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRetractable%20leashes%20offer%20very%20little%20control%20of%20the%20dog%20and%20may%20cause%20serious%20injuries%20if%20people's%20fingers%2Farms%2Flegs%20get%20caught%20in%20the%20leash%20and%20the%20leash%20is%20snapped%20taut%20by%20the%20dog%2C%26quot%3B%20veterinarian%20Pavlovsky%20says.%20They%20can%20also%20be%20difficult%20to%20manage%20with%20bigger%20or%20stronger%20dogs%2C%20particularly%20in%20situations%20where%20quick%20recall%20is%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-leashes%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757706736000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c474b1f9db348adc0b68d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-leashes%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20tested%20the%20best%20dog%20leashes%20for%20everyday%20walks%20and%20training.%20Our%20top%20picks%20include%20hands-free%20and%20rope%20leashes%2C%20and%20those%20that%20curb%20pulling.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sorin%20McKnight%2CSophia%20Carlisle)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fpets%2Fbest-dog-leashes%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'COVID%20shot%20or%20Taylor%3F'%3A%20Charlie%20Kirk%E2%80%99s%20old%20post%20mocking%20pop%20star%20sparks%20outrage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757706571000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-123855312%2Cimgsize-900066.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fnfl%2Fnews%2Fcovid-shot-or-taylor-swift-charlie-kirks-old-post-mocking-the-pop-star-and-questioning-travis-kelces-health-has-sparked-outrage%2Farticleshow%2F123854733.cms%22%2C%2