s%20of%20experience%20as%20a%20premier%20stealth%20aircraft%20designer%20and%20its%20tech%20from%20the%20next-generation%20fighter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20US%20selected%20Boeing%20over%20Lockheed%20Martin%20to%20build%20the%20Air%20Force's%20F-47%20stealth%20fighter%2C%20seen%20here%20in%20an%20artist%20rendering.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68c4554b183847aa39d6af65%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20US%20selected%20Boeing%20over%20Lockheed%20Martin%20to%20build%20the%20Air%20Force's%20F-47%20stealth%20fighter%2C%20seen%20here%20in%20an%20artist%20rendering.%3Cp%3EUS%20Air%20Force%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELockheed%20Martin%20this%20year%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboeing-wins-air-force-next-generation-air-dominance-fighter-contract-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20lost%20its%20bid%20for%20the%20sixth-generation%20F-47%20to%20Boeing%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20a%20move%20that%20dealt%20a%20blow%20to%20the%20company's%20long-held%20dominance%20in%20the%20stealth%20fighter%20game.%20Lockheed%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bdisappointed%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20soon%20announced%20its%20plan%2C%20with%20Taiclet%20saying%20the%20company's%20aim%20was%20to%20update%20the%20F-35%20so%20it%20could%20match%2080%25%20of%20the%20F-47's%20capabilities%20for%20half%20the%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaiclet's%20comments%20this%20week%20were%20the%20first%20indication%20of%20government%20interest%2C%20though%20US%20officials%20have%20not%20acknowledged%20any%20interest%20publicly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaiclet%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20at%20Lockheed%20Martin%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20still%20think%20sixth-generation%20aircraft%20should%20be%20developed%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20that%20he%20believes%20the%20upgraded%20F-35%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bincredible%20value%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20US%2C%20especially%20given%20that%20the%20sixth-generation%20program%20will%20take%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20in%20May%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-f-55-twin-engine-f-35-fighter-new-plane-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esaid%20he%20was%20interested%20in%20an%20upgraded%20F-35%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20he%20described%20something%20that%20went%20far%20beyond%20what%20Lockheed%20Martin%20has%20publicly%20described%3A%20An%20F-35%20that%20would%20have%20two%20engines%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20usual%20one.%20A%20former%20US%20Air%20Force%20pilot%20who%20was%20involved%20with%20the%20F-35%20program%20described%20that%20idea%20to%20Business%20Insider%20as%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etantamount%20to%20building%20a%20whole%20new%20aircraft%20and%20likely%20to%20take%20decades%20and%20incur%20huge%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaiclet%20said%20that%20the%20US%20could%20have%20around%201%2C000%20to%201%2C500%20fifth-gen-plus%20capable%20F-35s%20in%20the%20future%2C%20as%20two-thirds%20of%20the%202%2C300%20F-35s%20that%20have%20been%20ordered%20but%20not%20yet%20delivered%20are%20bound%20for%20the%20US%20and%20could%20be%20upgraded%20with%20sixth-generation%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20government%20has%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20interest%26quot%3B%20in%20discussing%20aircraft%20modernization%2C%20%26quot%3Ball%20the%20way%20up%20to%20the%20administration%20level%2C%20the%20White%20House%20level%2C%20and%20we're%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20that%20with%20them%2C%20and%20we're%20getting%20heard%2C%20we're%20hearing%20back%20and%20it's%20pretty%20active.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20said%20that%20if%20a%20contract%20is%20signed%20for%20the%20jet%20it%20may%20not%20be%20clear%20to%20investors%2C%20saying%20%26quot%3Bthe%20way%20to%20contract%20this%20will%20probably%20not%20be%20visible%20to%20folks%20because%20it%20will%20have%20so%20much%20classified%20content%20that%20it%20may%20not%