es%20beads%20or%20embellishments%20from%20old%20jewellery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESocial%20media%20has%20been%20her%20biggest%20stage.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20by%20posting%20crochet%20work%20online.%20Consistency%2C%20sharing%20behind-the-scenes%2C%20connecting%20with%20people%2C%20that%E2%80%99s%20how%20orders%20came%20in.%20Now%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20steady%20stream%20of%20queries%2C%20especially%20for%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20gone%20viral%20overnight%2C%20but%20it%20has%20grown%20steadily.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20keepsake%20that%20is%20full%20of%20soul%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Zainab%20Mukhtyar%2C%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20about%20intimacy%20and%20permanence.%20%E2%80%9CTraditional%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20lovely%2C%20but%20they%20fade%20away%20within%20hours.%20With%20crochet%2C%20you%20can%20preserve%20that%20special%20moment.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20keepsake%20that%20couples%20can%20hold%20on%20to%2C%20just%20like%20their%20memories%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Zainab's%20crochet%20brand%20focuses%20on%20the%20emotional%20value%20of%20each%20varmala.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015539.954-1756931176-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496052%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EZainab%E2%80%99s%20crochet%20brand%20focuses%20on%20the%20emotional%20value%20of%20each%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fzains_story%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZain%E2%80%99s%20Story%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20Manya%2C%20Zainab%E2%80%99s%20idea%20didn%E2%80%99t%20come%20from%20a%20specific%20request.%20It%20was%20born%20out%20of%20her%20own%20reflections%20on%20weddings%20and%20memory.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20one%20moment.%20It%20was%20just%20the%20thought%20that%20you%20could%20preserve%20your%20special%20day%20in%20a%20more%20meaningful%20way.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20I%20began%20curating%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%2C%20she%20says%2C%20has%20been%20steadily%20growing.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20off%20immediately%2C%20but%20now%20I%20get%20new%20queries%20almost%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%20Each%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3Etakes%20two%20to%20three%20days%20to%20make%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20number%20of%20flowers%20and%20the%20design.%20She%20uses%20acrylic%20yarn%20and%20adds%20beads%20to%20bind%20the%20flowers%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Zainab%2C%20the%20appeal%20lies%20in%20the%20emotional%20value.%20%E2%80%9CNothing%20goes%20to%20waste.%20The%20flowers%20don%E2%80%99t%20wilt.%20It%E2%80%99s%20handmade%20with%20love%20and%20care%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20couples%20can%20keep%20forever.%20I%20fe